          "description": "My name is Bridgette Pierre-Saint,I am a RN. I have worked with Nicholas  Cortez,  my Nursing  Recruiter for over three  years.  He is such an amazing  Recruiter.  Once I communicate  my needs as far as assignments, he finds them almost immediately.  I have never worked with such  a knowledgeable  Recruiter  before. He takes the time  to explain whatever I am not sure of. He gets  me the best rates and he always  makes sure that I feel comfortable with my assignments.\nI wish all Recruiters were like him.",
