          "description": "I was referred to this agency by a friend at a time when I was very unhappy at my previous job. Grant Thomas and my recruiter Sam Thompson were extremely helpful from the very start. They listened to my concerns, what I was looking for in a job and really pulled through to find me the best position at the highest possible pay rate. Anytime I have a question or need help with something both Sam and Grant have gone above and beyond to help me. I would recommend WCS to any nurse looking for employment. It is a great company and they really care about you as an individual. I am now so much happier at my job and I am learning and have an opportunity to grow as an RN.",
